attributes.title: Recurve Bow (Archery)
attributes.description:
Created on February 24, 2010 by mberns on Sourcemap.org:

A recurve bow is one a the few types of bows used in competitive archery.  The limbs can be made of full wood, but nowadays they are often made of a wood, carbon composite.  The riser is made of aluminum.
